<h2 class="gem-c-heading  gem-c-heading--mobile-top-margin  " id="details-title">Details</h2>


<div aria-labelledby="details-title">
  
<div class="gem-c-govspeak govuk-govspeak direction-ltr" data-module="govspeak">
      <div class="govspeak">
<p><abbr title="Local authority">LA</abbr> Welfare Direct bulletins provide advice, guidance and information that affects Housing Benefit (<abbr title="Housing Benefit">HB</abbr>) and other areas of <abbr title="Department for Work and Pensions">DWP</abbr>, including:</p>

<ul>
  <li>policy changes</li>
  <li>good practice</li>
  <li>reminders</li>
</ul>

<div class="call-to-action">
<p>These publications replace our <a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/collections/housing-benefit-direct"><abbr title="Housing Benefit">HB</abbr> Direct newsletters</a> and <a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/collections/housing-benefit-for-local-authorities-bulletins">General Information Bulletins</a>.</p>
</div>

</div>
</div>

